# Worktrees created by `cursed delegate --worktree` live under .cursed/.
# Also catches other local-only artifacts (goldens captures, scratch
# scripts). The same line is auto-appended by ensureGitignoreLine() on
# first delegate; pre-adding it keeps unrelated diffs clean.
.cursed/
.claude/worktrees/
